Ranger Help for: trail signs
=============================

SYNTAX:      signs
             trailsigns
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     5
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to read trail markers that have been left
in the current room by other Rangers. Trail markers contain short
messages left by fellow Rangers as directions, warnings, or notes.
Only Rangers can see and read these markers. If no markers are present
in the room, the skill will report that no signs have been found.
